Note on the Noesis Native SDK
-----------------------------

This crate links against the Noesis Native SDK (libNoesis), which is closed-
source commercial software distributed by Noesis Technologies S.L. under their
own End User License Agreement. The Noesis SDK is **not** included in this
repository; it must be obtained separately from https://www.noesisengine.com/
and supplied at build time via the NOESIS_SDK_DIR environment variable.

The MIT terms above apply only to the source code in this repository. Use,
distribution, and licensing of binaries built against the Noesis SDK are
governed by the Noesis EULA you accepted when obtaining the SDK.
